body.description: One soft tissue is all it takes to show you care. Reach for gentle, indulgently soft Kleenex Ultra Soft Tissues for a friend, a stranger or yourself. With the perfect balance of softness and strength, Kleenex facial tissues are durable with 3-ply thickness, delivering a strong facial tissue to lock in moisture. Strong & soothing facial tissues are perfect for makeup smudges, sniffles and sneezes, children’s messy faces and more. Just use and toss. Stock up and save! Keep tissues on hand to care for family, company and yourself during cold and flu season, allergy season, back-to-school and holidays. And as always, Kleenex Pack come in a variety of colors and designs that blend beautifully into your home décor. Place Pack in the living room, kitchen, bathrooms, bedrooms and office. Kleenex disposable facial tissues have been there for happy tears and stuffy noses since 1924. Kimberly-Clark is proud to provide $4 million through May 31, 2020, to support World Wildlife Fund’s efforts to protect forests and other critical ecosystems. ‘WWF’ and ‘World Wildlife Fund’ are WWF Registered Trademarks. 1986 Panda Symbol WWF.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 1, 2014
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great, Convenient, & Better Than Standard Kleenex, But Can't Pick Colors
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I am very happy with my Kleenex Ultra 8-pack, which is the Kleenex you expect, convenient, and better than standard Kleenex. Kleenex Ultra is nicer than Kleenex standard, which seems thicker, sturdier, and softer (but less absorbent if used for minor spills). I just put this on subscription every 2 months, is usually a good value, and very convenient to keep stocked. You get a variety of colors, which vary by shipment, and you might get multiple of the same design in a box. I have received 3 orders of this now, and am very happy.The main drawback is that you cannot pick your colors. You get a random selection, which is usually just fine. But there may be colors you dislike. You might end up with multiple of your least favorite design in a box. I once got several boxes where the sheets were not fully cut and would pull multiple and had to tear them, which I figure could happen at the store as well. I once noticed a slight funky smell when using a few boxes, which I am rather sensitive to, but it isn't always the case as I haven't noticed it recently.Overall, it is Kleenex Ultra, the same as you would find at the store (as far as I can tell), in a convenient box.

reviews.reviewText: There are only two kinds of tissues I will buy anymore, and this is one of them (I can't mention the other brand probably but it's very soft and puffy too). Wish I could pick the exact box colors since I'm kinda anal about what boxes go in what locations around our home, but I just buy a bunch and hope we have enough different colors.I review hundreds of products I buy on Amazon and rely on reviews from others a lot too to make my purchase decisions. I paid full price for these and always do and always will because they are great and worth every penny! I only rate an item 5 stars if I would pay full price for it or be willing to give it as a gift. I do give 1 star (since you can't give 0) to items which are so bad that I throw away, return for refund or wouldn't want even if free. I try to mention all the pros and cons of products. I have no affiliation with this company or any company for products I review, and my reviews are always totally my own (including any photos/videos). I hope my time spent reviewing this item helped in your decision. If it did, please vote "yes" below! Thanks!

If we cannot know the date of the rapture, why would Jesus tell us to watch for it?Mark 13:37And what I say unto you I say unto all, Watch.The rapture and second coming of Jesus are two totally different and separate events.The rapture happens at the beginning of the seven year tribulation period.The second coming happens at the end of the seven year tribulation period.Romans Road to SalvationRomans 3:10As it is written, There is none righteous, no, not one:Romans 3:23For all have sinned, and come short of the glory of God;Romans 5:8But God commendeth his love toward us, in that, while we were yet sinners, Christ died for us.Romans 5:12Wherefore, as by one man sin entered into the world, and death by sin; and so death passed upon all men, for that all have sinned:Romans 6:23For the wages of sin is death; but the gift of God is eternal life through Jesus Christ our Lord.Romans 10:9-119 That if thou shalt confess with thy mouth the Lord Jesus, and shalt believe in thine heart that God hath raised him from the dead, thou shalt be saved.10 For with the heart man believeth unto righteousness; and with the mouth confession is made unto salvation.11 For the scripture saith, Whosoever believeth on him shall not be ashamed.Romans 10:13For whosoever shall call upon the name of the Lord shall be saved.Romans 11:36For of him, and through him, and to him, are all things: to whom be glory for ever. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 23, 2014
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Regular high quality, and so CONVENIENT!!!
reviews.reviewText: I LOVE having enough Kleenex at home to pull out a replacement box anytime!These are the same 3-ply tissues you can buy at your local grocery store -- except that Amazon delivers them for you free of charge and even gives you a discount via Subscribe-and-Save! I LOVE having enough Kleenex at home to pull out a new one each time any of the boxes by the bed, or in the baths, or on the end tables in the living room or on the counter in the kitchen (can you tell hay fever is rampant in this house?) suddenly run dry, usually at very inconvenient moments.No more having to count how many are still left in the pantry before going shopping. No more temporarily stealing a mostly full box from elsewhere because there aren't any extras left in the pantry! (and then, of course, discovering I have to get up from my comfy chair when I start to sneeze and find the table nearby has sacrificed its box to another location!). Believe it or not, we use up a whole case each month. Just as I'm starting to wonder whether there will be enough left, another case arrives. There's plenty to take charge of in this world, and lots of claims on our energy and attention. This is one thing I no longer have to worry about!No compromises -- usual high quality, great convenience, and savings to boot -- what a deal!!!
